About Edmond M. Safra of  EMS CAPITAL LP



									
										   Edmond M. Safra is President at Ems Capital Lp and has been affiliated with Ems Capital Lp since June-2007. Ems Capital Lp is a hedge fund that manages 1.5 BN dollars in regulatory AUM and has 11 employees, of which 5 perform investment advisory functions. The managers's latest filing has disclosed 1BN in positions, which represents 71% of the manager's regulatory AUM.  For more on Ems Capital Lp including top positions, information on the investment process, service provider information, other key employees, real time performance, 13-F holdings and more visit the Fund Profile







