Capital Markets

Company Overview of EMS Capital LP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
EMS Capital LP is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It invests in public equity markets across the globe. The firm typically invests in long/short equity and value stocks of companies. It employs fundamental research to make its investments. The firm uses proprietary research to make its investments. EMS Capital LP was founded on June 26, 2007 and is based in New York City.


499 Park Avenue11th FloorNew York, NY 10022United StatesFounded in 2007



Phone: 212-891-2713

Fax: 212-891-2702








